00:10:44.200 --> 00:10:48.120
I'll take your temperatures and
prove that you're faking ill.

00:10:48.120 --> 00:10:49.680
We really have colds.

00:10:49.680 --> 00:10:52.820
Yeah. Let us go home early.

00:10:53.430 --> 00:10:54.520
Nope!

00:10:55.720 --> 00:10:56.520
