00:11:25.960 --> 00:11:28.800
A pen? Did you say a pen?!

00:11:28.800 --> 00:11:31.930
Does this look like a pen to you?!

00:11:33.020 --> 00:11:38.060
How... How stupid can you be?

00:11:39.790 --> 00:11:44.260
This thermometer actually
looks like a pen to you?!

00:11:45.500 --> 00:11:48.020
Then have a...

00:11:48.020 --> 00:11:49.350
better...

00:11:49.350 --> 00:11:50.990
look!

00:11:50.990 --> 00:11:52.400
Stab

00:12:03.290 --> 00:12:04.440
She's...

00:12:11.070 --> 00:12:13.010
Noriaki Kakyoin

00:12:14.320 --> 00:12:18.000
