00:12:37.370 --> 00:12:39.200
This isn't a woman's strength.

00:12:39.950 --> 00:12:43.850
I saw something unknown
crawling up from the floor earlier.

00:12:43.850 --> 00:12:45.210
Was it a Stand?

00:12:45.560 --> 00:12:47.750
Noriaki Kakyoin...

00:12:47.750 --> 00:12:51.040
Was he the one who cut my leg on the stairs?

00:12:51.040 --> 00:12:52.210
Precisely.

00:12:53.160 --> 00:12:54.830
Y-You're...

00:12:55.460 --> 00:12:58.050
Hey. Short time no see.

00:12:58.050 --> 00:13:02.070
