00:14:13.460 --> 00:14:14.340
Squish

00:14:14.950 --> 00:14:16.530
Don't try to act tough.

00:14:16.530 --> 00:14:19.400
I can see my finger marks on your forehead.

00:14:20.580 --> 00:14:24.350
If I go ahead and crush your
Stand's head like a melon,

00:14:24.850 --> 00:14:27.140
it looks like your head will be crushed, too.

00:14:29.740 --> 00:14:32.010
I'm gonna keep a grip on you for a while.

00:14:32.010 --> 00:14:34.280
I'll take you to the old man.

00:14:34.870 --> 00:14:37.340
I'm sure he'd love to meet you...

00:14:38.090 --> 00:14:41.260
And I'd like to know more about DIO myself.

00:14:48.590 --> 00:14:49.760
What?

00:14:49.760 --> 00:14:52.840
Green fluid is coming out of his Stand's hands?

00:14:53.550 --> 00:14:55.210
I already told you, Jojo...

00:14:55.210 --> 00:14:57.980
That you would regret this.

00:14:58.960 --> 00:15:02.220
Feel the attack of my Stand, Hierophant Green!

00:15:02.460 --> 00:15:04.680
Don't make any weird moves!

00:15:13.000 --> 00:15:15.190
Emerald Splash!

00:15:27.560 --> 00:15:29.080
What do you think?

00:15:29.080 --> 00:15:30.850
Emerald Splash...

00:15:31.240 --> 00:15:34.820
What looked like the bodily fluids
of my Stand, Hierophant Green,

00:15:34.820 --> 00:15:36.820
was a vision of destructive energy!

00:15:37.210 --> 00:15:39.430
It's pierced through your Stand's chest.

00:15:39.990 --> 00:15:42.970
Therefore, your insides
have been torn to shreds.

00:15:43.170 --> 00:15:45.810
And that nurse...

00:15:49.230 --> 00:15:50.810
Wh-What?

00:15:51.170 --> 00:15:54.490
I'm certain that I removed the Stand from her...

00:15:54.490 --> 00:15:56.110
I already told you...

00:15:56.470 --> 00:16:02.000
Attacking my Hierophant Green
would mean hurting her.

00:16:02.500 --> 00:16:07.610
My Stand can reach further than yours,
but it doesn't like open spaces.

00:16:07.610 --> 00:16:11.250
It prefers to hide within something.

00:16:12.020 --> 00:16:15.380
If you drag it out, it gets angry.

00:16:15.380 --> 00:16:19.980
That's why, when it came out
from her throat, it hurt her.

00:16:20.950 --> 00:16:23.100
It's your fault, Jojo!

00:16:23.100 --> 00:16:24.550
This is your responsibility!

00:16:24.760 --> 00:16:26.800
This is your fault, Jojo!

00:16:26.800 --> 00:16:28.560
You did this!

00:16:28.870 --> 00:16:33.870
If you had let me kill you in the first place,
this nurse wouldn't have been hurt.

00:16:37.610 --> 00:16:39.020
You're trying to stand up?

00:16:40.050 --> 00:16:41.900
But how sad...

00:16:41.900 --> 00:16:43.640
If I were to compare you to something,

00:16:43.640 --> 00:16:46.160
it'd be a sandbag in front of of a boxer.

00:16:46.160 --> 00:16:50.370
You stood back up only to be hit again.

00:16:48.430 --> 00:16:54.410
Menacing

00:16:54.660 --> 00:16:56.810
I, Jotaro Kujo,

00:16:57.360 --> 00:17:00.000
am labeled a punk.

00:17:00.880 --> 00:17:04.120
Ramen

00:17:01.140 --> 00:17:04.120
I tend to overdo it with my opponents in fights,

00:17:04.120 --> 00:17:06.640
so much that some are still in the hospital.

00:17:07.220 --> 00:17:09.310
There was one idiot teacher who was all talk,

00:17:09.310 --> 00:17:13.180
so I taught him a lesson,
and he hasn't come back to school.

00:17:14.330 --> 00:17:17.300
At restaurants that served me lousy food,

00:17:17.300 --> 00:17:20.270
I leave without paying the bill all the time.

00:17:20.940 --> 00:17:22.020
But...

00:17:22.020 --> 00:17:23.560
Even I

00:17:24.830 --> 00:17:27.160
know nauseating evil when I see it.

00:17:27.570 --> 00:17:31.680
Evil is when you use the
weak for your own gain,

00:17:31.680 --> 00:17:33.780
and crush them under your foot.

00:17:35.420 --> 00:17:37.290
Especially a woman!

00:17:38.470 --> 00:17:40.410
That is exactly what you've done!

00:17:41.720 --> 00:17:47.950
Your Stand isn't visible to the
victim or the law. Therefore...

00:17:48.900 --> 00:17:50.550
I shall judge you!

00:17:51.250 --> 00:17:52.500
Evil?

00:17:52.500 --> 00:17:54.060
There, you are wrong.

00:17:54.590 --> 00:17:56.570
Evil refers to the loser.

00:17:56.570 --> 00:17:58.560
Justice refers to the victor.

00:17:58.560 --> 00:18:01.070
The last man standing!

00:18:01.070 --> 00:18:04.320
The method doesn't matter!

00:18:12.220 --> 00:18:14.040
Grab

00:18:14.350 --> 00:18:16.790
The loser is the evil one.

00:18:16.970 --> 00:18:18.470
And now, the final blow!

00:18:19.910 --> 00:18:22.290
What? The loser is evil?

00:18:22.520 --> 00:18:26.010
Emerald Splash!

00:18:26.670 --> 00:18:29.180
Well, in that case...

00:18:31.750 --> 00:18:32.600
What?!

00:18:33.150 --> 00:18:36.480
Impossible! He shrugged off the Emerald Splash?

00:18:36.480 --> 00:18:39.020
...you're the evil one after all!

00:18:56.580 --> 00:18:57.870
The one who'll be the judge is...

00:18:58.330 --> 00:19:00.500
my Stand!

00:18:58.830 --> 00:19:00.500
Smash!

00:19:08.350 --> 00:19:10.950
What a powerful Stand...

00:19:12.450 --> 00:19:16.520
You just caught it by surprise
and hurt its chest a little.

00:19:17.050 --> 00:19:19.400
Lucky for me it's not a weak Stand,

00:19:19.400 --> 00:19:23.060
but I have a feeling it'll become more violent.

00:19:23.650 --> 00:19:25.490
That was close.

00:19:28.950 --> 00:19:31.400
She should be fine once her wounds are treated.

00:19:32.360 --> 00:19:34.070
What was that? A gas explosion?

00:19:34.070 --> 00:19:35.490
It came from the nurse's office!

00:19:35.490 --> 00:19:37.380
None of you leave the classroom!

00:19:37.380 --> 00:19:38.790
I'll leave the rest to them.

00:19:39.550 --> 00:19:41.250
I'm ditching school today.

00:19:41.720 --> 00:19:46.000
I've got to have him explain
some things about DIO.

00:20:00.250 --> 00:20:02.980
Hierophant Green

00:20:01.040 --> 00:20:02.980
Noriaki Kakyoin

00:20:10.650 --> 00:20:12.050
Ping

00:20:16.410 --> 00:20:19.840
Jotaro's totally thinking
about me at school right now!

00:20:19.840 --> 00:20:23.310
I felt like I had a connection
with my son just now.

00:20:23.310 --> 00:20:24.620
I'm not thinking about you.

00:20:25.600 --> 00:20:27.000
Jotaro!

00:20:27.000 --> 00:20:30.550
Wh-What about school? And who is that?

00:20:30.550 --> 00:20:32.740
H-He's covered in blood!

00:20:32.740 --> 00:20:36.570
D-Don't tell me... you did that?

00:20:36.570 --> 00:20:38.340
It's got nothing to do with you.

00:20:39.260 --> 00:20:41.140
I'm looking for the Old Man.

00:20:41.910 --> 00:20:44.690
Sucks having to find him in such a huge house.

00:20:44.690 --> 00:20:47.410
I think your grandfather's in the tea room,

00:20:47.410 --> 00:20:49.110
with Mister Avdol.

00:20:51.680 --> 00:20:53.050
Oh, Jotaro...

00:20:53.050 --> 00:20:55.560
You won't tell me anything.

00:20:55.560 --> 00:20:57.870
Even though I... I...

00:20:57.870 --> 00:21:00.520
worry about you so much.

00:21:01.720 --> 00:21:05.440
But I know that, deep down,

00:21:05.440 --> 00:21:08.130
you're a sweet boy.

00:21:08.440 --> 00:21:09.280
Hey.

00:21:09.280 --> 00:21:10.130
Yes?

00:21:11.720 --> 00:21:13.980
You look a little pale this morning.

00:21:14.490 --> 00:21:15.510
Are you all right?

00:21:18.690 --> 00:21:22.060
Yay! Fine, thank you!

00:21:25.680 --> 00:21:27.090
I knew it.

00:21:28.630 --> 00:21:31.780
Well, this is no good. It's too late for him.

00:21:31.990 --> 00:21:33.910
He's not going to make it.

00:21:33.910 --> 00:21:36.320
He'll die in the next few days.

00:21:37.660 --> 00:21:40.440
Jotaro, it's not your fault.

00:21:40.440 --> 00:21:44.320
Look. The reason that this
man swore loyalty to DIO

00:21:44.320 --> 00:21:48.730
and came to kill you...

00:21:49.650 --> 00:21:50.710
is right here!

00:21:52.160 --> 00:21:54.550
What the hell is that?!

00:23:25.010 --> 00:23:27.020
Next Episode Preview

00:23:27.910 --> 00:23:30.600
This isn't good at all... At this rate...

00:23:30.600 --> 00:23:32.530
Sometimes having a cold isn't so bad.

00:23:32.530 --> 00:23:34.990
I don't really understand, either.

00:23:34.990 --> 00:23:37.760
This is the one thing I feared most!

00:23:37.760 --> 00:23:40.030
Tell me how we should deal with this!

00:23:38.030 --> 00:23:40.030
Episode 3:

00:23:38.030 --> 00:23:40.030
The Curse of DIO